videos.headline: Haley Jones spins for acrobatic finish for Stanford
videos.description: Stanford's Haley Jones makes her way to the basket and spins through heavy traffic for a sweet layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Haley Jones spins for acrobatic finish for Stanford) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alexus Dye swoops in for Tennessee and-1 bucket
videos.description: Alexus Dye navigates through the paint to put up a nice reverse and-1 layup around the Stanford defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Alexus Dye swoops in for Tennessee and-1 bucket) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ashten Prechtel gets hot from deep in the 4th quarter
videos.description: Stanford's Ashten Prechtel starts feeling it from downtown as she hits three consecutive 3-point shots in the fourth quarter.
